│ The relevant section of the code for the bug is the transformation logic in `visitSelectInst`, specifically the block starting at line 3870. The issue lies in the handling of the │
│ `nsz` flag when canonicalizing the `select` instruction based on the `fcmp` predicate. The transformation assumes that the `nsz` flag allows it to freely swap operands and invert │
